order=darkgray}} The contestant received positive critiques and was ultimately declared safe.\n:{{Color box|cornsilk|border=darkgray}} The contestant received  critiques but was ultimately declared safe.\n:{{Color box|lightpink|border=darkgray}} The contestant received negative critiques but was ultimately declared safe.\n:{{Color box|lightsalmon|border=darkgray}} The contestant received negative critiques but had immunity from elimination.\n:{{Color box|tomato|border=darkgray}} The contestant was in the bottom two.\n:{{Color box|red|border=darkgray}} The contestant was eliminated.\n:{{Color box|Gainsboro|border=darkgray}} The contestant returned as a guest for that episode.\n\n==Lip-syncs==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" border=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\" \n|-\n!Episode\n!colspan=\"3\"|Contestants\n!Song\n!Eliminated\n|-\n|1\n|Akashia\n|vs.\n|Victoria \"Porkchop\" Parker\n|[[Supermodel (You Better Work)]]<br /><small>([[RuPaul]])</small>\n|style=\"background: lightblue\"|'''Victoria \"Porkchop\" Parker'''\n|-\n|2\n|Akashia\n|vs.\n|Tammie Brown\n|[[We Break the Dawn]]<br /><small>([[Michelle Williams (singer)|Michelle Williams]])</small>\n|style=\"background: lightblue\"|'''Tammie Brown'''\n|-\n|3\n|Akashia\n|vs.\n|Shannel\n|[[The Greatest Love of All]]<br /><small>([[Whitney Houston]])</small>\n|style=\"background:lightpink\"|'''Akashia'''\n|-\n|4\n|Jade \n|vs.\n|Rebecca Glasscock\n|[[Would I Lie to You? (Eurythmics song)|Would I Lie To You?]]<br /><small>([[Eurythmics]])</small>\n|style=\"background: lightblue\"|'''Jade'''\n|-\n|5\n|BeBe Zahara Benet\n|vs.\n|Ongina\n|[[Stronger (Britney Spears song)|Stronger]]<br /><small>([[Britney Spears]])</small>\n|style=\"background:lightblue\"|'''Ongina'''\n|-\n|6\n|Rebecca Glasscock\n|vs.\n|Shannel \n|[[Shackles (Praise You)]]<br /><small>([[Mary Mary]])</small>\n|style=\"background: lightgreen\"|'''Shannel'''\n|-\n|8\n|Bebe Zahara Benet \n|vs.\n|Nina Flowers\n|[[Cover Girl (RuPaul song)|Cover Girl (Put the Bass in Your Walk